reviewText: Great DVD and came right on time my Husband loved it since he is a big Mopar Fan.
Fun to watch with my mopar360 club.
QUALITY DVD. WILL BE ENJOYED BY ALL WHO VIEW IT.
I received the product. When I went to watch it the sound would cut in and out. Also the picture kept freezing up and then play. The reason for the low rating is I was not able to watch the video.
This movie is great for any Die hard MOPAR guy. It has alot of great cars and stories of Mopar fans.
